## [1.0.0] - 2025-01-30

### Added
- Initial release of CoinFeedly trading journal
- Complete trading dashboard with customizable widgets
- User authentication and registration system
- Trade entry and management system
- Performance analytics and visualizations
- Multi-currency support (30+ currencies)
- Stripe payment integration for Pro/Elite subscriptions
- PostgreSQL database integration
- Email verification system
- Password reset functionality
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop

### Features
- **Dashboard Widgets:**
  - Equity Curve visualization
  - Performance Metrics display
  - Drawdown Analysis
  - Trade List with filtering
  - Trade Calendar with visual P&L

- **Trading Features:**
  - Comprehensive trade tracking (entry/exit prices, P&L, notes, tags)
  - Support for long and short positions
  - Image attachments for trade screenshots
  - Real-time performance calculations

- **User Management:**
  - Session-based authentication
  - Email verification required
  - Profile management
  - Currency preference settings

- **Subscription Management:**
  - Free tier (5 trades limit)
  - Pro tier ($29/month - unlimited trades)
  - Elite tier ($49/month - premium features)
  - 7-day free trial for paid plans